      <reaction compartment="compartment_984" fast="false" id="reaction_1067676" metaid="metaid_41" name="IL6:IL6R-2 binds IL6ST-2" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Soluble IL6ST (sgp130) binds to circulating Interleukin-6 (IL6) bound to the soluble form of IL6 receptor alpha (IL6:IL6R-2), preventing binding to IL6ST (gp130) on the plasma membrane, thereby specifically inhibiting IL6 trans-signaling (Jostock et al. 2001).</p>
        </notes>
