      <reaction compartment="compartment_876" fast="false" id="reaction_1067667" metaid="metaid_56" name="IL6 binds IL6R" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Interleukin-6 (IL6) site I interacts with the Interleukin-6 receptor subunit α (IL6Rα), which is non-signaling but ligand-specific (Taga et al. 1989).</p>
        </notes>
